<br>
Yes HE is one of the more UBER warriors on any server but wasnt this nerf brought about due to the most UBER monks across servers. Put the comparison and you will see that a Warrior can solo even better than a monk with that type of equipment IF he can fight mobs that come solo. Self Haste for him is 61% to our 81% but hes got all the bells and whistles to help him solo .<br>
<br>
Fungi is BY far worth the neg stats for soloing PERIOD. Unless you can get a Lunar Fungus Tunic.<br>
