<br>
The nerf was their way, albeit a bit extreme, of correcting those mistakes.<br>
<br>
Druids, wizards, necros, shamans, beatlords are classes which were designed with the ability so solo in mind. Comparing their solo ability to that of a monk is comparing apples to oranges.<br>
<br>
